      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 that exemplifies mechanical perfection. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering razor-sharp throttle response via individual throttle bodies and optimized dual-VANOS timing. The high-revving powerplant is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The exterior finish remains in showroom state, while the suspension geometry is perfectly dialed for track-inspired turn-in without sacrificing street compliance. A turn-key masterpiece for the purist collector.",
