      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule: a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage under a premium soft cover. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather seats remain supple and free of any bolster wear or creasing, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It features a comprehensive service history with every scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or inclement weather exposure. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example suited for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection. Complete documentation, two sets of keys, and the original window sticker are included in the sale.",
